      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P1SHME 17
      *-------------------*
     C                     TIME           WTIME
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         KEYRRN 100
     C                     EXSR #SB400
      *
